             sworn. - Last Monday, between two and three o'clock, nearly opposite <placeName id="t17980418-18-crimeloc81">St. Dunstan's church, in Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17980418-18-crimeloc81" type="placeName" value="St. Dunstan's church, in Fleet-street"></interp>
