             sworn. - (Produces the pocket book). I am a constable: I received the pocket-book from the prosecutor, and took charge of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Campbell. This is the pocket-book that was taken from me.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am innocent of the charge.</p>
